Name: Sanae Toumaden X2
About the game: ☆This is Touhou project fan game. Sanae! The Super Gensokyo Miko! Intro A Mega X Touhou Fangame With No X again. Story A moon rocket flew from the Scarlet Devil Mansion At a speed of 90,000 km/s. Two people got off at Hakugyokurou. There was hardly time for half-humans to ride. That Yakumo lot are so competitive— They fired off an interceptor missile! System Jump and Slash Platform Action Game. Beat all Bosses and Get New Ability. Enemies are weak to one Ability. After the Cannon shooted, then you get few more stage. All stage is Rogue-unlike stage. Stage design by human. Rogue-unlike upgrade system. Anything you get in stage will not lost. Soul-unlike attack system. It don't have stamina limit. You can attack unlimited times if you like.
